comment: LO SLA shows Collison (SAC) makes contact with Lowry's (TOR) arm that affects his ball control before he starts his upward motion.
Barnes (SAC) makes incidental contact with Patterson (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR.
LO SLA shows Lowry (TOR) pushes Temple (SAC) out of bounds.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor that the ball was last touched by TOR was confirmed.
Carroll (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Gay (SAC) that does not affect his post move and shot attempt.
Gay (SAC) dislodges Carroll (TOR), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
[Observable in enhanced video] Carroll (TOR) moves his pivot foot.
Gay (SAC) and Valanciunas (TOR) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Valanciunas (TOR) makes marginal contact with Cousins (SAC) on the perimeter.
Cousins (SAC) sets the screen on Carroll (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Cousins (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] DeRozan (TOR) moves his pivot foot.
Collison (SAC) makes contact with Lowry's (TOR) body that affects his jump shot attempt and his ability to land.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor that Lowry's shot attempt was a 3pt FG was confirmed.

The free throw is missed with 27.4 seconds remaining, and after the rebound attempt is tipped, Cousins (SAC) gains possession with 26.4 seconds remaining, at which point the shot clock is correctly started. Sacramento calls a timeout with 26.2 seconds remaining.
A timeout was called before Collison (SAC) took any additional steps.
Lowry (TOR) makes incidental contact with Collison (SAC) that does not affect his SQBR.
The 24-second shot clock expired before the ball hit the rim.
Patterson (TOR) sets the screen on Collison (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

The on-court referees noticed a clock malfunction on the inbounds play and correctly triggered an instant replay. After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that the clock should have started when Cousins (SAC) tips the ball and run to 0:00.00 before Rossâ€™ (TOR) shot was released.
